      <body>I almost wonder if it wouldn't be even more helpful to include more with the error messages.  Like an inspection of the controller's local variables.  My thought is to [eventually] post some prototype error pages so we can decide on a reasonable color scheme.  mod_rails style might work, too.  They're nice.
